<h1 id="1-前期准备工作"><a href="#1-前期准备工作" class="headerlink" title="1. 前期准备工作"></a>1. 前期准备工作</h1><ol>
<li><p>安装 node.js</p>
</li>
<li><p>安装 git，创建 github 账号</p>
</li>
<li><p>安装 Hexo</p>
 <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p> <img src="https://mymapdepot.zrc520.com/HexoDepot/ArticlePicture/file002.png" alt="安装图片"></p>
<p> <a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/">Hexo 官网</a></p>
</li>
</ol>
<h1 id="2-构建框架"><a href="#2-构建框架" class="headerlink" title="2. 构建框架"></a>2. 构建框架</h1><ol>
<li><p>建立一个文件夹</p>
 <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir &lt;folder&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li><p>初始化</p>
 <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p> <img src="https://mymapdepot.zrc520.com/HexoDepot/ArticlePicture/file001.png" alt="tu2"></p>
</li>
<li><p>安装依赖</p>
 <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>安装需要插件（后续还需要安装其他插件）</p>
 <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ol>
<h1 id="3-Hexo-基本指令"><a href="#3-Hexo-基本指令" class="headerlink" title="3. Hexo 基本指令"></a>3. Hexo 基本指令</h1><pre><code><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo &lt;man&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">clean     Remove generated files and cache.</span><br><span class="line">config    Get or set configurations.</span><br><span class="line">deploy    Deploy your website.</span><br><span class="line">generate  Generate static files.</span><br><span class="line">server    Start the server.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</code></pre>
<h1 id="4-更换主题"><a href="#4-更换主题" class="headerlink" title="4. 更换主题"></a>4. 更换主题</h1><ol>
<li>下载主题<ul>
<li>根目录执行(不建议)：   <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone -b master https://github.com/jerryc127/hexo-theme-butterfly.git themes/butterfly</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li>去官网拉取<br>  <a href="https://github.com/jerryc127/hexo-theme-butterfly">点击这里</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<br>

<ol start="2">
<li><p>安装主题<br>将主题文件名改为</p>
</li>
<li><p>安装插件：</p>
 <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-pug hexo-renderer-stylus --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ol>
<h1 id="配置弹窗"><a href="#配置弹窗" class="headerlink" title="配置弹窗"></a>配置弹窗</h1><pre><code><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install node-snackbar</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

修改主题文件

<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">snackbar:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">position:</span> <span class="string">bottom-left</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">bg_light:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;#49b1f5&#x27;</span> <span class="comment"># The background color of Toast Notification in light mode</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">bg_dark:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;#1f1f1f&#x27;</span> <span class="comment"># The background color of Toast Notification in dark mode</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</code></pre>
<h1 id="配置全局吸底音乐播放器"><a href="#配置全局吸底音乐播放器" class="headerlink" title="配置全局吸底音乐播放器"></a>配置全局吸底音乐播放器</h1>   <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install --save hexo-tag-aplayer</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


]]></content>
